{"tid":1649002,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［新口號］香港人！！！ 還拖！！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-12T12:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T14:53:35.000Z","uid":41181,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3209d6faaf400018cee9ae3c0b4a035d5155e00f","tid":1649002,"uid":41181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:54:56.000Z","msg":"話說今日做環保撚唔搭車行路，見到隔黎有個絲打一聽到人嗌「香港人」，佢就應「還拖」，由尖咀嗌到出深水埗都仲嗌得勁響。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後行過深水埗，有個呀叔唔知係咪聽完之後開始幫拖，係路邊同啲遊行人士講：「依加啲狗擺到明係係攪啲香港人，打你地，你地仲嗌得咁斯文做乜鳩？」成班香港人一齊叫還拖件事真係好撚型。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得呀叔真心有道理，都比人踩到上心口，我地係要反抗，但係具體內容要點做？我感覺「反抗」可以只係一種心態，但係「還拖」比我感覺更加實在地要以牙還牙 以眼還眼。我好相信文字嘅魔力，我希望多啲人可以帶頭嗌還拖，大家潛移默化，希望再有手足比一兩隻狗㩒低嘅時候，可以大家上去還拖，唔好只係口口聲聲話反抗，但係就一味拎住部手機拍片。"},{"pid":"98a7e6c97ea57deb91a59a8c58f8f40b204ede39","tid":1649002,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0895409eee97c3abc1be14aed260711857c695e8","tid":1649002,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:57:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"85304785c3de541bedee2bb535f53f924af00e9c","tid":1649002,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/3DeFV2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2F3DeFV2.jpeg&h=11fde298&s={SIZE}\" />"}